<P>
Play Review 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA081690-0149 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 262693 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 16, 1990, Thursday, Ventura County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Ventura County Life; Part J; Page 8; Column 1 
