<P>
Open Sundays through Thursdays till 11, Fridays and Saturdays till midnight. 
(714) 498-TROP. A yuppie joint with charm. Sit leisurely under the thatched 
roof and sip tropical drinks while viewing the pier and surfers below. The most 
memorable feature, though, is found in the ladies room: a mural of Tarzan that 
lets out a yell in the bar when you pull down the Ape Man's loincloth.JAMES M. 
GOMEZ 
