<P>
TRAINING CENTER TO FUND SCHOLARSHIPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Amateur Sports Training Center of Fountain Valley has donated $15,000 to 
the UC Irvine women's volleyball scholarship fund. 
</P>
<P>
The donation will fund two scholarships. The Amateur Sports Training Center is 
a nonprofit corporation that helps young athletes with training, coaches and 
traveling arrangements for competition. 
</P>
